channel.title: [562] Element-X [Updated] Fullscreen/HD + All Bosses + All 23 Skills Working
channel.description:
Hello, This is my first server. I Hope you guys will enjoy it and play it with a lot fun! ;)
~---~---~---~---~---~---~
* Started SoulWars. * Music while playing * Godwars. * PVP drops only from pk such as vesta's morrigans statius etc. * Item on item, item on object, item on npc examples for new coders. just search the base. * Anti flood * Had it run 3 days without a restart * Most skills work ( You can hunt on several monsters and construction works with interfaces! ) * A unique home same as on my never released 317 ' infinity ' * Lots of portals and npcs to take you somewhere to take out lots of commands. * The world map button opens a map with teleport buttons * Options, house button opens your house interfaces! * Fully working canoe stations! ( I put one at the river at home ) * You can hunt on rabbits, kebbits, birds and chinchompas using a knife on the first two gets you the best pking food there is! so hunter is a moneymaking skill the bird snare and box trap actually create the item and you have to click it to get your prey. Shaking box f.e. from the chins * Farming based on geo's but added the drops from npc's * I took out ::item and made the server work without spawning! * An awesome economy server and 1600x xp per hit * Free for all PK npc at home with interfaces * Summoning works and so does the interface it's coded with the dismiss button and the face of your familiars you just have to add a button or a command to open the interface, I'm not spoonfeeding you guys. * Alot of bosses, specials, trainingplaces etc; -Jad -Armadyl -Giant Mole -Kind Black Dragon -Bandos -Corporeal Beast -Skeletal Horror -Zamorak -Saradomin -Barrelchest -Kalphite Queen -Mutant Tarn -Chaos Elemental -Balance Elemental -Dessous +Much More * You can't get dragon in shops from rune on everything gets dropped by boss npc's and other though guys! * There is way more and I left some hidden easter eggs in there too for the people that'll use it they'll thank me alot.
